description: Support for Bower has been dropped, use NPM or another package manager instead.
Support for CommonJS modules has been dropped, use the ES module import instead.

The default export has been changed to a named export. Import parseTemplate with a named import instead of calling the parse method from the previous default object. See https://github.com/bramstein/url-template/releases/tag/v3.0.0 for details.
Some functions that were already marked as private are now no longer available
